snippet.title: Tannenberg - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.tannenberggame.com

The developers behind the FPS Verdun, M2H and Blackmill Games, announce a new title in their realistic WW1 1914-1918 series: Tannenberg.

The standalone expansion takes place on the Eastern Front and will be available later this year on PC via Steam. Make sure to add the game to your wishlist:  http://store.steampowered.com/app/633460
